      <title>美国说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/deported-venezuelans-in-el-salvador-prison-not-at-risk-of-torture-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府拒绝担心被指控的委内瑞拉帮派成员根据《外国敌人法》驱逐出境，在臭名昭著的萨尔瓦多监狱中有酷刑的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/deported-venezuelans-in-el-salvador-prison-not-at-risk-of-torture-us-says</guid>
